file_content.text: [You attempt to shut down the missile launch sequence using the logistics computer.]
[Unfortunately, General Ortol has activated the emergency locks, preventing the missile batteries from shutting down.]
[However, this logistics computer can be used to alter the trajectory of the missiles.]
[You reconfigure the missile trajectories to target the Imperial fleet.]
[You reconfigure the missile trajectories to target one of Cademimu's uninhabited moons.]
